gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nets 106, Rockets 104
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nets defeated the Rockets, 106-104. Cam Thomas led the way for the Nets with 37 points, along with three rebounds and three assists, while Mikal Bridges added 19 points, five rebounds and three steals in the victory. Jalen Green tallied 19 points (4-9 3pt. FG) and 10 rebounds for the Rockets in the losing effort. The Nets improve to 18-27 on the season, while the Rockets fall to 21-24.
